name: As the holy folk of yore used to say, "Hoc modo"
description:
I typed "this is the way" into Google translate and that's what it came up with, so who knows what it actually says. It could be, ‘People called Romanes they go the house’ for all I know.

Look at these Fetts! Or Mando's. Or whomever they are, whichever the clan. Sexy, sultry, the whole shebang.
